description:
Casey is a Pokémon Trainer and a big fan of the Electabuzz Baseball Team.
Casey`s Father and Grandfather cheered the anthem to the Electabuzz baseball team as they saw Casey off as she started her Pokémon trainer adventure.
Casey started her Pokémon journey in New Bark Town where she choose Chikorita as her starting Pokémon. Chikorita shares Casey`s love for Baseball and wears a headband with the Electabuzz baseball team logo on.
name: Nanako
